    "Name": "Shadow Wolf SDW-12",
    "Details": "The Shadow Wolf SDW-12 is a 20-ton stealth recon BattleMech produced by Maltex Corporation beginning in 3068, built around Stealth Armor powered by a left-torso Guardian ECM Suite to mask its approach. Three Small Lasers and two Streak SRM 2s spread across the head, center torso, and right torso provide a close-range punch disproportionate to its weight class. A head-mounted TAG laser designates targets for allied artillery support, extending the mech's battlefield impact well beyond its own weapons.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Sensors</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.97</color></b>",
